{"type":"message","id":"d2ae4736","parentId":"6f6c888c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:17:03.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has made decisions:\n1. Keep numbering (00, 01, 02...)\n2. German date format DD-MM-YYYY (10-04-2026)\n3. Hybrid folder structure for projects (flat index files, separate attachments folder if needed)\n4. MOCs distributed in each main folder (not just centralized) for faster LLM navigation\n\nI should:\n1. Confirm these decisions\n2. Update the folder structure proposal with these preferences\n3. Continue with the grilling process - next question should be about link conventions or naming conventions\n\nLet me update the structure and ask the next question.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**Entscheidungen bestätigt:**\n- ✅ Nummerierung bleibt (00, 01, 02...)\n- ✅ Deutsches Datum: `10-04-2026` (gespeichert in MEMORY.md)\n- ✅ Hybrid-Struktur für Projekte\n- ✅ MOCs verteilt (jeder Ordner hat seine eigene Navigation)\n\n---\n\n**Aktualisierte Ordnerstruktur:**\n\n```\nSecondBrain/\n├── 00-Meta/\n│   ├── Templates/\n│   ├── Scripts/\n│   └── Config/\n│\n├── 01-Daily/\n│   ├── 10-04-2026.md\n│   ├── 10-04-2026-meeting-xyz.md\n│   └── _MOC-Daily.md          ← Übersicht über Tagesnotizen\n│\n├── 02-Projects/\n│   ├── _MOC-Projects.md        ← Alle Projekte, Status, Priorität\n│   ├── SecondBrain-Reorganization.md\n│   ├── WikiLinks-Implementation.md\n│   └── _Attachments/           ← Nur wenn Assets nötig\n│       ├── SecondBrain-Reorganization/\n│       │   └── diagram.png\n│       └── WikiLinks-Implementation/\n│           └── architecture.svg\n│\n├── 03-Knowledge/\n│   ├── _MOC-Knowledge.md\n│   ├── Concepts/\n│   │   ├── _MOC-Concepts.md\n│   │   ├── Zettelkasten.md\n│   │   └── WikiLinks.md\n│   ├── How-To/\n│   │   └── _MOC-HowTo.md\n│   └── People/\n│       └── _MOC-People.md\n│\n└── 99-Archive/\n    └── (dein aktuelles Vault als Backup)\n```\n\n---\n\n**Frage 11 – Naming Conventions:**\n\nWie benennen wir Dateien?\n\n- **Option A:** **Kebab-Case** – `second-brain-reorganization.md` (Standard, URL-freundlich)\n- **Option B:** **CamelCase** – `SecondBrainReorganization.md` (kompakt, aber schwer lesbar)\n- **Option C:** **Title Case mit Spaces** – `Second Brain Reorganization.md` (natürlich, aber Leerzeichen in Links müssen escaped werden)\n- **Option D:** **UUID + Name** – `a1b2c3-Second-Brain-Reorganization.md` (für automatische Sortierung, aber ugly)\n\n**Empfehlung:** Option A – Kebab-Case. Leerzeichen in WikiLinks (`[[Second Brain]]`) funktionieren, aber Dateinamen ohne Leerzeichen sind robuster für Scripts und URLs.\n\nWas bevorzugst du?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":24057,"output":715,"cacheRead":3072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775812592957}}
