 Notizen / Brainstorming\n- \n\n## Ressourcen / Links\n- \n\n## Verwandte Projekte\n- \n\n## Erstellt\n{{date:DD-MM-YYYY HH:mm}}\n\n## Letzte Aktualisierung\n{{date:DD-MM-YYYY HH:mm}}\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/SecondBrain/00-Meta/Templates/Project.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_VWgQJI9kzVv2DVw57C0x1YZE","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ndate: {{date:DD-MM-YYYY}}\ntype: knowledge\ncategory: concept  # concept | how-to | reference\ntags: [knowledge]\n---\n\n# {{title}}\n\n## Definition / Zusammenfassung\n<!-- 1-3 Sätze: Was ist das? -->\n\n## Details\n<!-- Ausführliche Erklärung -->\n\n## Beispiele\n<!-- Konkrete Beispiele -->\n```\nBeispiel hier\n```\n\n## Verwandte Konzepte\n- \n\n## Quellen / Referenzen\n- \n\n## Erstellt\n{{date:DD-MM-YYYY HH:mm}}\n\n## Letzte Aktualisierung\n{{date:DD-MM-YYYY HH:mm}}\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/SecondBrain/00-Meta/Templates/Knowledge.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_OYKqMtZHGPycdwkIl4hC54fa","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ndate: {{date:DD-MM-YYYY}}\ntype: decision\ntags: [decision, adr]\nstatus: proposed  # proposed | accepted | rejected | deprecated\n---\n\n# {{title}}\n\n## Kontext\n<!-- Was ist die Situation? -->\n\n## Entscheidung\n<!-- Was wurde entschieden? -->\n\n## Konsequenzen\n<!-- Was ändert sich? Positive und negative Effekte -->\n\n## Alternativen betrachtet\n<!-- Was gab es noch? Warum nicht? -->\n- \n\n## Verwandte Entscheidungen\n- \n\n## Erstellt\n{{date:DD-MM-YYYY HH:mm}}\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/SecondBrain/00-Meta/Templates/Decision.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":8357,"output":1101,"cacheRead":40704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50162,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775814494500}}
