{"type":"message","id":"0e915951","parentId":"6df5fa0f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:51:51.544Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_A5nNLjbn2zyJKmt1WbYwWtqf","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ndate: 2026-04-08\ntime: 01:25\ntype: session\ntitle: Session 2026-03-22\ncategory: project\ntags:\n  - todo\n  - coding\n  - openclaw\n  - ai\n  - architecture\n  - project\n  - session\nrelated_notes:\n  - 📝 [[2026-03-22]] (83 gemeinsame Begriffe: 2026, mission, control)\n  - 📝 [[2026-03-26]] (23 gemeinsame Begriffe: 2026, session, files)\n  - 📝 [[2026-04-02-FINAL]] (17 gemeinsame Begriffe: 2026, continued, session)\nrelated_count: 5\nsession_id: 2026-04-08-0125\nagent: andrew-main\nuser: parzival\nstatus: active\nsource_file: 2026-03-22.md\ndecisions: none\ntodos: extracted\ncode_blocks: 0\n---\n\n# Session 2026-03-22\n\n## Zusammenfassung\n**4. Full Integration of User's Original Files**\nIntegrated all 19 files provided by the user, adapted with Linear dark theme styling:\n\n## Offene Aufgaben\n- ✅ Complete TypeScript Types (Task, Project, Memory, Doc, Agent, Activity, Calendar, Office)\n- ✅ Full taskStore with all CRUD operations + reordering + AI task claiming\n- ✅ Full activityStore with filtering, unread counts, connection status\n- ✅ Complete KanbanBoard with 5 columns (added 'todo' column)\n- ✅ KanbanColumn with stats (estimated hours, high priority count)\n- ✅ TaskCard with full feature set\n- ✅ CreateTaskDialog with all fields\n- ✅ ActivityFeed with icons, filters, unread indicators\n- ✅ useRealtime hook for SSE\n- ✅ useDebounce hook for search\n- ✅ AI Agent Service with task handlers (research, coding, docs)\n- ✅ All API Routes: /api/tasks, /api/tasks/[id], /api/realtime, /api/projects, /api/memories, /api/docs, /api/agents\n- ✅ Complete DB Schema with all 7 tables\n**Key Improvements from Integration:**\n- 5 Kanban columns instead of 4 (backlog → todo → in_progress → review → done)\n- Task reordering within columns\n- Task deletion capability\n- Activity logging to database\n- Full search & filter capabilities\n- Project management store\n- Memory/document/agent API endpoints ready\n**Theme Adaptation:**\n- All components converted to Linear dark theme\n- bg-[#0a0a0a] backgrounds\n- border-white/[0.06] subtle borders\n- Purple (#8B5CF6) accents for primary actions\n- Color-coded columns (blue for in_progress, yellow for review, green for done)\n**Status:**\n- All 19 original files successfully integrated\n- Application ready for testing at http://localhost:3000/tasks\n- SQLite database persistent\n- Real-time sync working\n- AI Agent polling every 5 seconds\n**User Preference:**\n- German language for responses\n- GUI/clickable interfaces preferred over CLI\n- Linear-style dark design aesthetic\n- TypeScript strict mode\n\n---\n\n## Original\n\n```\n\n[23 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775814711529}}
{"type":"message","id":"c123efa8","parentId":"0e915951","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:52:21.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Diese Session hat viel Inhalt! Das ist eine echte Projekt-Session über Mission Control v2. Ich sollte diese als Projekt-Note migrieren, nicht als Daily Note. Es gehört zu einem Projekt (Mission Control v2).\n\nLass mich diese Session als Projekt-Note migrieren.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Das ist eine echte Projekt-Session! Ich migriere sie als Projekt:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_LNJ1zHIGAGYEAxx95Ca4hOWr","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ndate: 08-04-2026\ntime: 01:25\ntype: project\nstatus: completed\ntags: [project, mission-control, typescript, nextjs, ui]\ncategory: software-project\nsession_id: 2026-04-08-0125\nagent: andrew-main\nuser: parzival\nsource_file: 2026-03-22.md\n---\n\n# Projekt: Mission Control v2 Integration\n\n## Zusammenfassung\nIntegration aller 19 vom User bereitgestellten Dateien mit Linear Dark Theme Styling. Vollständige TypeScript-Implementierung mit allen Stores, Komponenten und API-Routen.\n\n## Ergebnisse\n\n### ✅ Implementiert\n\n**TypeScript Types**\n- Task, Project, Memory, Doc, Agent, Activity, Calendar, Office\n\n**Stores**\n- Full taskStore mit CRUD + Reordering + AI Task Claiming\n- Full activityStore mit Filtering, Unread Counts, Connection Status\n\n**UI Komponenten**\n- KanbanBoard mit 5 Spalten (backlog → todo → in_progress → review → done)\n- KanbanColumn mit Stats (geschätzte Stunden, High Priority Count)\n- TaskCard mit Full Feature Set\n- CreateTaskDialog mit allen Feldern\n- ActivityFeed mit Icons, Filters, Unread Indicators\n\n**Hooks & Services**\n- useRealtime hook für SSE\n- useDebounce hook für Search\n- AI Agent Service mit Task Handlern (research, coding, docs)\n\n**API & Datenbank**\n- Alle API Routes: /api/tasks, /api/tasks/[id], /api/realtime, /api/projects, /api/memories, /api/docs, /api/agents\n- Complete DB Schema mit allen 7 Tabellen\n- SQLite persistent\n- Real-time sync working\n- AI Agent polling every 5 seconds\n\n### 🎨 Theme Anpassungen\n\n- Linear Dark Theme\n- bg-[#0a0a0a] backgrounds\n- border-white/[0.06] subtle borders\n- Purple (#8B5CF6) accents für Primary Actions\n- Color-coded columns (blue für in_progress, yellow für review, green für done)\n\n## User Preferences ( dokumentiert )\n\n- German language for responses\n- GUI/clickable interfaces preferred over CLI\n- Linear-style dark design aesthetic\n- TypeScript strict mode\n\n## Status\n\n- ✅ Alle 19 originalen Dateien erfolgreich integriert\n- ✅ Application ready für Testing\n- ✅ http://localhost:3000/tasks\n\n## Verwandte Sessions\n\n- [[Session-2026-03-26|Session 2026-03-26]] (23 gemeinsame Begriffe)\n- [[Session-2026-04-02|Session 2026-04-02]] (17 gemeinsame Begriffe)\n\n## Erstellt\n08-04-2026\n\n## Letzte Aktualisierung\n08-04-2026\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/SecondBrain/02-Projects/Completed/mission-control-v2-integration.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1836,"output":807,"cacheRead":56320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58963,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775814711549}}
