{"type":"message","id":"82ca7320","parentId":"b6ed03dd","timestamp":"2026-04-10T12:12:38.321Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Der Nutzer will, dass ich prüfe, ob die Daten im ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Ordner wirklich vollständig migriert sind. Ich soll also:\n\n1. Schauen was im ECC-Ordner noch ist\n2. Vergleichen mit dem was wir migriert haben (scripts und templates)\n3. Prüfen ob es noch weitere wichtige Dateien gibt die wir übersehen haben\n\nLass mich das systematisch machen.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_OtA8g4xY9hpDtLDMwzAVDiQw","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Detaillierte Analyse des ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Ordners\nWrite-Host \"=== ECC-SECOND-BRAIN-FRAMEWORK ANALYSE ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n$eccPath = \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\vault-archive\\Main_Obsidian_Vault\\Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert\"\n\n# 1. Komplette Struktur anzeigen\nWrite-Host \"`n1. KOMPLETTE STRUKTUR:\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nGet-ChildItem -Path $eccPath -Recurse -File | \n    Select-Object FullName, @{N='SizeKB';E={[math]::Round($_.Length/1KB,2)}} |\n    Sort-Object FullName\n\nWrite-Host \"`n`n2. WAS WIR MIGRIERT HABEN:\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"   ✅ scripts/ -> 00-Meta/Scripts/ecc-framework/\"\nWrite-Host \"      - sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1\"\nWrite-Host \"      - auto-backup.ps1\"\nWrite-Host \"      - drift-detection.ps1\"\nWrite-Host \"      - ecc-stability.ps1\"\nWrite-Host \"`n   ✅ templates/ -> 00-Meta/Templates/\"\nWrite-Host \"      - Decision Template.md\"\nWrite-Host \"      - Project Template.md\"\nWrite-Host \"      - Session Template.md\"\n\nWrite-Host \"`n3. WAS NOCH IM ECC-ORDNER IST (nicht migriert):\" -ForegroundColor Red\n$subdirs = @('00-Dashboard', '00-Inbox', '01-Projects', '01-Sessions', '02-Areas', '03-Resources', '04-Archive', '05-Daily', '05-Templates', 'config', 'Dataview', 'Decisions', 'ecc-vault', 'lib', 'Patterns', 'Projects', 'SecondBrain', 'Skills', 'snippets')\n\nforeach ($dir in $subdirs) {\n    $path = Join-Path $eccPath $dir\n    if (Test-Path $path) {\n        $fileCount = (Get-ChildItem -Path $path -File -Recurse -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue).Count\n        if ($fileCount -gt 0) {\n            Write-Host \"   📁 $dir/ ($fileCount Dateien)\"\n            # Zeige die ersten 3 Dateien\n            Get-ChildItem -Path $path -File -Recurse -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object -First 3 Name | ForEach-Object {\n                Write-Host \"      - $($_.Name)\"\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}","workdir":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":124734,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124734,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775823120969}}
