{"type":"message","id":"89f95a47","parentId":"1b12dd8e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:07:16.683Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_qHUB0ZYIu2PPUbAqhAiBwvrJ","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== CORE SYSTEM (aktiv) ===\n\r\nName                  SizeKB Typ   \r\n----                  ------ ---   \r\ncmd-backup.ps1          9,32 Script\r\ncontext-switch.ps1      5,17 Script\r\nECC-Utilities.psm1     10,76 Modul \r\nEncryption.psm1         7,83 Modul \r\neval-runner.ps1         8,92 Script\r\nexample-usage.ps1       6,52 Script\r\nMermaidGenerator.psm1   7,88 Modul \r\n\r\n\r\n\n=== ARCHIV (Referenz) ===\n\r\nPfad                                  SizeKB\r\n----                                  ------\r\nREADME.md                               4,23\r\nconfig\\drift-config.yaml                4,08\r\nconfig\\eval-template.yaml               4,18\r\nconfig\\stability-config.yaml            3,13\r\nscripts\\auto-backup.ps1                17,16\r\nscripts\\drift-detection.ps1            12,88\r\nscripts\\ecc-stability.ps1              15,53\r\nscripts\\sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1  22,08"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":564,"aggregated":"=== CORE SYSTEM (aktiv) ===\n\r\nName                  SizeKB Typ   \r\n----                  ------ ---   \r\ncmd-backup.ps1          9,32 Script\r\ncontext-switch.ps1      5,17 Script\r\nECC-Utilities.psm1     10,76 Modul \r\nEncryption.psm1         7,83 Modul \r\neval-runner.ps1         8,92 Script\r\nexample-usage.ps1       6,52 Script\r\nMermaidGenerator.psm1   7,88 Modul \r\n\r\n\r\n\n=== ARCHIV (Referenz) ===\n\r\nPfad                                  SizeKB\r\n----                                  ------\r\nREADME.md                               4,23\r\nconfig\\drift-config.yaml                4,08\r\nconfig\\eval-template.yaml               4,18\r\nconfig\\stability-config.yaml            3,13\r\nscripts\\auto-backup.ps1                17,16\r\nscripts\\drift-detection