{"type":"message","id":"5391e6a2","parentId":"4eef9738","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:21:51.094Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_0TjcjKa1uNyiujgIKiEYKS8v","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== CORE SYSTEM (5 essenzielle Komponenten) ===\n\r\nName               SizeKB Typ   \r\n----               ------ ---   \r\ncmd-backup.ps1       9,32 Script\r\ncontext-switch.ps1   5,17 Script\r\nECC-Utilities.psm1  10,76 Modul \r\nEncryption.psm1      7,83 Modul \r\neval-runner.ps1      8,92 Script\r\n\r\n\r\n\n=== ARCHIV (vollst�ndig indexiert) ===\n\r\nPfad                                  SizeKB\r\n----                                  ------\r\nREADME.md                               5,03\r\nconfig\\drift-config.yaml                4,08\r\nconfig\\eval-template.yaml               4,18\r\nconfig\\stability-config.yaml            3,13\r\nmodules\\example-usage.ps1               6,52\r\nmodules\\MermaidGenerator.psm1           7,88\r\nscripts\\auto-backup.ps1                17,16\r\nscripts\\drift-detection.ps1            12,88\r\nscripts\\ecc-stability.ps1              15,53\r\nscripts\\sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1  22,08"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":506,"aggregated":"=== CORE SYSTEM (5 essenzielle Komponenten) ===\n\r\nName               SizeKB Typ   \r\n----               ------ ---   \r\ncmd-backup.ps1       9,32 Script\r\ncontext-switch.ps1   5,17 Script\r\nECC-Utilities.psm1  10,76 Modul \r\nEncryption.psm1      7,83 Modul \r\neval-runner.ps1      8,92 Script\r\n\r\n\r\n\n=== ARCHIV (vollst�ndig indexiert) ===\n\r\nPfad                                  SizeKB\r\n----                                  ------\r\nREADME.md                               5,03\r\nconfig\\drift-config.yaml                4,08\r\nconfig\\eval-template.yaml               4,18\r\nconfig\\stability-config.yaml            3,13\r\nmodules\\example-usage.ps1               6,52\r\nmodules\\MermaidGenerator.psm1           7,88\r\nscripts\\