{"type":"message","id":"3c35fdb6","parentId":"131915e8","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:23:01.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Der Nutzer möchte, dass ich die 12 losen Dateien im vault-archive Root analysiere. Ich sollte systematisch vorgehen und jede Datei gründlich analysieren, vergleichen und bewerten.\n\nLass mich die Dateien im Root-Verzeichnis von vault-archive/Main_Obsidian_Vault/ auflisten und analysieren.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**[Analysiere die 12 losen Dateien im vault-archive Root...]**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_FiCzDjRbNyoNuNcpyQ4ny5qH","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Liste alle losen Dateien im vault-archive Root (nicht in Unterordnern)\n$rootPath = \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\vault-archive\\Main_Obsidian_Vault\"\n\nWrite-Host \"=== LOSE DATEIEN IM ROOT ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nGet-ChildItem -Path $rootPath -File | \n    Select-Object Name, \n        @{N='SizeKB';E={[math]::Round($_.Length/1KB,2)}},\n        @{N='Extension';E={$_.Extension}} |\n    Sort-Object SizeKB -Descending"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":4463,"output":244,"cacheRead":171776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":176483,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775830967828}}
{"type":"message","id":"06c254f0","parentId":"3c35fdb6","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:23:02.344Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_FiCzDjRbNyoNuNcpyQ4ny5qH","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== LOSE DATEIEN IM ROOT ===\n\r\nName                                    SizeKB Extension\r\n----                                    ------ ---------\r\nOpenClaw Harness Diagnosis.pdf          177,57 .pdf     \r\nOpenClaw_Harness_Diagnosis.md             58,4 .md      \r\nharness_redesign_specification.md        39,24 .md      \r\nobsidian-second-brain-implementation.md  18,05 .md      \r\nopenclaw_config_specification.md         11,98 .md      \r\ncode all claude.txt                      10,63 .txt     \r\nsession-summary.md                       10,14 .md      \r\nAI_AGENT_WORK_INSTRUCTION.md              8,35 .md      \r\nharness-integration-plan.md               7,33 .md      \r\ncreate-dirs.ps1                           0,86 .ps1     \r\nWelcome.md                                 0,2 .md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":455,"aggregated":"=== LOSE DATEIEN IM ROOT ===\n\r\nName                                    SizeKB Extension\r\n----                                    ------ ---------\r\nOpenClaw Harness Diagnosis.pdf          177,57 .pdf     \r\nOpenClaw_Harness_Diagnosis.md             58,4 .md      \r\nharness_redesign_specification.md        39,24 .md      \r\nobsidian-second-brain-implementation.md  18,05 .md      \r\nopenclaw_config_specification.md         11,98 .md      \r\ncode all claude.txt                      10,63 .txt     \r\nsession-summary.md                       10,14 .md      \r\nAI_AGENT_WORK_INSTRUCTION.md              8,35 .md      \r\nharness-integration-plan.md               7,33 .md      \r\ncreate-dirs.ps1                           0,86 .ps1     \r\nWelcome.md                                 0,2 .md","cwd":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":17758309823